PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of CAROLINE GRACE GRANGER of Hillier, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Farm Credit Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Deborah Sherren (Jones) Whale.
